## Project Type
Course creator landing pages ($2,999), 7-day delivery.

## Technical Gates
- Lighthouse: Perf ≥85, A11y ≥90, Best-Practices ≥95, SEO ≥90.
- Page weight <2 MB; use WebP/AVIF + lazy loading.
- Events: `cta_clicked`, `form_submit`, `pricing_view` (IO threshold ≈0.3; fire once and disconnect).

## Business Gates
- Extract 10–15 production-grade components into `/components/vault/`.
- Month-3 targets: 60+ components, ≥70% reuse. 

## A11y/UX
- Keyboard navigable; visible focus; proper aria; CTA hit targets ≥44×44.

